title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show JULY-02-2013 TUES

The Glenn Beck Radio Show JULY-02-2013 TUES







The Glenn Beck Program

          
Listen to The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET         

      

      
The Glenn Beck Program - 07/02/2013


Tuesday, July 02, 2013 11:52 AM



Glenn and the guys discuss Obama's warning to the Africans...
   that they can't have big homes or big houses..
     what is he talking about?

 Also talks about how the redistribution of wealth is in full display,

 and the government's reasons for putting an NSA facility is Utah.

 Buck Sexton joins the guys to discuss  the latest on the chaos in Egypt.

 And Mike Broomhead joins to discuss the Arizona firefighters deaths.

 And why does  Pat think Rand Paul is a communist? 


        Tune in to find out.
